# goal-probe credential backstop (#874 plan step 2) — the primary store is
# out-of-repo ($HOME/.goal-probe-credentials/); these entries are
# defense-in-depth against operator error copying a token into a worktree.
# See .github/scripts/README-goal-probe.md § Credential handling.
.goal-probe-credentials/
*-oauth-token.txt

# goal-probe leg-capture backstop (#874 plan step 2 fix batch, M10) — raw
# credential-adjacent capture files (stdout/stderr transcripts) from the
# run-book's legs (a)/(c)/(g) are disposable and should never be committed;
# the probe worktree itself is disposable and should never be `git add`ed,
# but this is defense-in-depth in case a capture lands somewhere tracked.
leg-*.jsonl
leg-*.stderr.log
leg-*.log

# Agent scratch — keep out of git status
.tmp/
/[A-Za-z][A-Za-z]sers*
/[A-Za-z]:*
# /*[Tt]emp* intentionally removed (RF4): over-matched template.md, templates/, attempt.js.
# Primary mangle shapes are covered by /[A-Za-z]:* and /[A-Za-z][A-Za-z]sers* above.
/var*folders*
/[Rr][Uu][Nn][Nn][Ee][Rr]*[Tt][Ee][Mm][Pp]*
